Breeding adult (Eastern).description: Meadowlarks have yellow chests with a black "V" similar to Dickcissels, but they are much larger and stockier than Dickcissels, with shorter tails, white outer tail feathers, and longer, thinner bills.

Female.description: Female House Sparrows are stockier with a shorter and blunter bill than Dickcissels. They also do not have a black mustache line or a yellow eyebrow like Dickcissels.
